tech_rep_description: a modified M9 salt medium containing 68 mM phosphate buffer (pH 7), 18.6 mM NH4Cl, 8.6 mM NaCl, 2 mM MgSO4, and 100 µM CaCl2 with a trace element solution containing Na3-citrate at 51 µM, ZnSO4 at 7 µM, MnCl2 at 5 µM, CuSO4 at 4 µM, FeSO4 at 36 µM, H3BO3 at 5 µM, NaMoO4 at 137 nM, and NiCl2 at 84 nM
